text: Katerina Valkova (born 6 February 1996) is a Czech volleyball player. She played at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2016 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for TJ Ostrava. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Czech volleyball players
